		$gui->addContent('<p>Purchasing a modification is just as simple as purchasing a pod, however, instead of giving the modification a name, you chose which one of your team pods you wish to install it on from the dropdown list, and click submit. The mod will then be installed on said pod, and you\'ll be well on your way to becoming race-ready!');
		$gui->addContent('<p align="center"><img src=images/manual/mod.png></p>');
