		$gui->addContent("<center><img src=images/manual/podracer_intro.jpg></center>");
		
		$gui->addContent('<p>So, you want to be a Podracer? Well congratulations! Reading this manual is the FIRST step to joining the elite ranks of those guys who race pods!<p>Now, you may be asking yourself, "Voice, I want to be come a Podracer, but I don\'t know where to start."<p>Well, by reading this manual, you\'re lying to me! You are already where you need to be to be a full-fledged Podracer! The first thing you need to do is figure out what role you want to play in Podracer.<p> We have 3 choices here in the Lyarna Circuit, and they are:');
		$gui->addContent('<br />1. <a href=?1>The Team Owner</a>');
		$gui->addContent('<br />2. <a href=?2>The Team Member</a>');
		$gui->addContent('<br />3. <a href=?3>The Spectator</a>');
		$gui->setTitle ("So, You want to be a Podracer!");
